pressive effects while at the same time minimizing risk of disease reactivation.', 'Synergism', 'Siponimod has not been studied in patients receiving drugs that can prolong the QT interval.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/150024/', '', 'Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Belumosudil, Ozanimod, Teprotumumab, Emapalumab, Ravulizumab, Pegcetacoplan, Eculizumab, Sutimlimab', 'Siponimod, Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Belumosudil, Teprotumumab, Emapalumab, Ravulizumab, Pegcetacoplan, Eculizumab, Sutimlimab', 1767369485);
